name: Finn
description: Finn is a recruit at the Night's Watch. He joined the Night's Watch the same day as Gared Tuttle.
biography: Finn originates from the area around Raventree Hall, controlled by House Blackwood in the Riverlands. House Blackwood is one of the few major houses outside of the North that continues to worship the Old Gods of the Forest, and Finn does so.
